{"id":159384,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/澳广-福建七名访民据报在美使馆前服毒自杀/","date":"2011-06-09T02:00:18Z","modified":"2011-06-09T02:00:18Z","title":"澳广 | 福建七名访民据报在美使馆前服毒自杀","content":"<div>\n<p>福建七名访民据报在美使馆前服毒自杀</p>\n<p>星岛日报报道，北京的美国驻华大使馆门口，前日有七名来自福建的访民企图集体服毒自杀，但很快便被大使馆外的中国警卫人员制止。.</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<p>2011 年 06 月 08 日</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3238387.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/decrease.gif\" alt=\"Decrease\" title=\"Decrease\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3238387.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/standard.gif\" alt=\"Standard\" title=\"Standard\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3238387.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/increase.gif\" alt=\"Increase\" title=\"Increase\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/mailto/mailto-nojs_query.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3238387.htm&#038;presname=/ra\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/email.gif\" alt=\"Email\" title=\"Email\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/printfriendly.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3238387.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/print.gif\" alt=\"Print\" title=\"Print\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3238387.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/favourite.gif\" alt=\"Favourite\" title=\"Favourite\" /></a></p>\n<p>星岛日报报道，北京的美国驻华大使馆门口，前日有七名来自福建的访民企图集体服毒自杀，但很快便被大使馆外的中国警卫人员制止。</p>\n<p>其中一名访民表示，他们选择在美国大使馆做出激烈行为，是想唤起国际社会关注中国弱势社群的处境。</p>\n<p>中国访民到外国大使馆伸诉，早几年也发生过，但做出集体自杀这样的激烈行为还是首次。</p>\n</div>\n</t